Linda ‘Prokid’ Mkhize will be laid to rest on Sunday at the Westpark Cemetery.  Prokid died on Wednesday, August 8 after suffering a seizure. The 37-year-old  has been hailed as one of Soweto’s best and a pioneer in kasi-style hip-hop. The funeral service is  be held at University of Johannesburg’s Soweto Campus and will proceed to West Park cemetery where he will be buried.  